{"tid":259591,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"麻枝准 × 熊木杏里","createTime":"2017-05-27T05:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T17:28:38.000Z","uid":49057,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4ebaf921b77dbaa21e3e8a53ad8fca604d1027","tid":259591,"uid":49057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:21:29.000Z","msg":"話說之前麻枝准同やなぎなぎ都出過隻專輯『終わりの惑星のLove Song』，大家都應該有聽過，就唔多提 <br />\n<br />\n而尋日Key既youtube頻道upload左呢首bus stop，聽完覺得唔錯就黎分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8d2RyotAGn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8d2RyotAGn4&d=d66SdBlJp1VENnazzFlDU4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7e552b47\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8d2RyotAGn4</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube個簡介到有下面條link，一睇先知原來麻枝准又有新野搞 <br />\n麻枝 准&times;熊木杏里『Long Long Love Song』 <br />\n歌同PV都係維持返麻枝既風格，有少少抑鬱催淚feel <br />\n令我自己比較在意既就係入面有首歌叫『汐のための子守歌』，介紹係&quot;渚に描いた 君の名は今でも&quot;，未聽都知係催淚野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麻枝寫劇本係垃圾d，但係寫歌真係一流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://key.soundslabel.com/long_long_love_song\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkey.soundslabel.com%2Flong_long_love_song&d=d66SdBlJp1VENnazzFlDU4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6e75a8a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://key.soundslabel.com/long_long_love_song</a>"},{"pid":"44acd27ffa0d68adf3ddd61ed8dd52b9b46f46bb","tid":259591,"uid":57122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"希望唔係遺作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af0d8dff27b2f92abdf673b78a39ce9471c3fdf","tid":259591,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"畫好靚"},{"pid":"aaf521f986772db11ba76c0d2f6409badd7d97ad","tid":259591,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:30:46